    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained 2018 Premium SUV is the perfect blend of luxury and reliability. The exterior retains a deep, glossy finish, showing only the minor road wear consistent with careful, responsible use. Inside, the leather upholstery remains supple and free of tears, smoke-free, and paired with a pristine dashboard and fully functional tech suite. Mechanically, it stands in solid health with a comprehensive service history, a smooth-shifting transmission, and tires with plenty of tread remaining. Garage-kept and recently detailed, this vehicle offers a 'turn-key' experience for a buyer seeking quality without the new-car price tag.",
